.container-fluid
  .row
    .col-md-12
      .text-heading
        .text-heading-label Name
        | {{project.title}}
      .text-heading(ng-if="project.description")
        .text-heading-label Description
        | {{project.description}}
      .btn-actions: .btn-group.btn-group-sm
        a.btn.btn-primary-clear(project-edit="project") Edit
      hr
  .row
    .col-md-4.col-md-push-6
      <p><b>Users that have access to this project.</b></p>
      <p>Tou can share access to the project with your collaborators, giving them specific access scope.</p>
    .col-md-6.col-md-pull-4
      .panel.panel-default
        .panel-heading Users
        .panel-body
          div.list-group.list-group-panel
            a.list-group-item(ng-repeat="user in project.users", user-edit="project" user-edit-model="user") {{user.username}}
              i.pull-right.subtitle {{user.role}}
            a.list-group-item(user-add="project"): b.text-primary + add user

   .row
    .col-md-4.col-md-push-6
      <p><b>API Consumers Credetials.</b></p>
      <p>To request Gandalf from an API client you need to create them separate keys. They should be send as HTTP Basic Auth login and password on each request to Gandalf.</p>
    .col-md-6.col-md-pull-4
      .panel.panel-default
        .panel-heading API Consumers Credentials
        .panel-body
          div.list-group.list-group-panel
            a.list-group-item(ng-repeat="consumer in project.consumers", consumer-edit="project", consumer-edit-model="consumer") {{consumer.description}}
            a.list-group-item(consumer-add="project"): b.text-primary + create consumer


   .row: .col-md-6
    button.btn.btn-danger(project-delete="project") Delete project

  p: br


